query:
SELECT
                    id,
                    account_id,
                    quota_type,
                    event_type,
                    event_payload as "event_payload: Value",
                    event_time as "event_time: DateTime<Utc>"
                FROM account_quota_events
                WHERE ($1::bigint IS NULL OR id > $1)
                  AND ($2::bigint IS NULL OR id <= $2)
                ORDER BY id
